scalation pattern from T-008@20260425T183959Zd and the sibling T-013@20260425T183959Za. The artistic-intent companion document (`docs/cypherclaw-sampler-artistic-intent.md`) is the remaining CCS-033 sibling and is left for a follow-up subtask.\n./src/cypherclaw/__init__.py:    FirstBootAnnouncer,\n./src/cypherclaw/__init__.py:    \"FirstBootAnnouncer\",\nBinary file ./src/cypherclaw/__pycache__/first_boot.cpython-311.pyc matches\nBinary file ./src/cypherclaw/__pycache__/__init__.cpython-311.pyc matches\n./src/cypherclaw/first_boot.py:class FirstBootAnnouncer:"}
